Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I have personally discovered, \Nright here, in our school, we have a promising skiing genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, it's tiresome... Right, Taru?{/boring/dull}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On such occasions, \NI like to gaze at Iyona-chan to kill time.{he just says "at such times, I stare/admire/observe iyona"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute, Iyona-chan...
