Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more than that!{/very much}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Edojo Skimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, we did well!{/succeeded}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru. \NIf it weren't for your magic, I'd never become a hero!{/thanks to your magic, I'm a hero}
