Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening. Iyona-chan and I have already planned \Nto do some love divination after this!{/I'm taking iyona for love fortune telling from now on - not sure why she says "iyona ha watashi ga" - it's as though iyona is performing love divination on rui or the other way around, but not "together"; upd: nevermind - rui is going to be fortune telling for iyona, that's what it is}
