Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui-chan is famed \Nfor having the most accurate divinations. {lit: fortune telling is reputed with hitting well/come true often}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need a developed sixth sense.{/I wonder if I have a reikan - "ability to sense the supernatural (esp. ghosts, etc.)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I do, per se...{really unsure if this is what she means, acting that conceited is not like rui at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Honmaru-kun, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wee you bedder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I go take a sneak peek at divination!{/I go see fortune telling}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to concentrate, \Nso nobody else is permitted into here!{/it would be a distraction so I forbid further entrance}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Skimaru-sensei, we need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond? Anybody got a diamond?{lit is "guy who stops the diamond" but I've no clue what's this about and idc tbh}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're doing love divination, \Nmaybe they're talking about the guys they like...{/I wonder if there's a boy she likes}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting under my skin!{/can't get it out of my head/I'm curious/obsessed/impatient}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a veranda, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Secretly checking on Iyona-chan \Nfrom outside the window sounds like a solution.{/doesn't seem bad either}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh hey, gonna go to the toilet real quick! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H7B0800&}Got it, toilet.{guess, sou? ii toire? itto ire? TLC? maybe it's something about his turn in cards or w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-san, this is the "Sevens" row.{still unsure what they are playing, also previously we've seen the "7" row is already full}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage one of operation - \Ncomplete success!{/first phase went well}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm here on a mission!{/But there's no time to get faint-hearted/rejoice - no clue what he means, lit is "doing something, it's not the case", deepl has it "I don't have time for this." TLC?} {Aurelius: 5:38: I'm hearing,  なんてやってる場合じゃないんだ！\NThe DeepL translation is pretty standard albeit a little general.\NHonmaru's essentially saying something like " I can't just stand here and succumb to the cold. I've got to move/got a mission to fulfill "\N" I've got no time to lose! " could also work. \NIt's up to you if you want to be more specific or not.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind that window is Iyona-chan!{/on the other side of/across ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also so damn high out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How come this tiny curb is all I have? {really unsure what he means, lit is "why do I have to go to such a place" TLC?} {5:51: I'm hearing こんなとこ行かなきゃなんないのかよ\NHonmaru's essentially saying something like "Do I really have to go all the way over there!?"\NHe's basically become more apprehensive now that he realizes what he has to do.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't matter!{/however}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything for Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:05:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is wide open!{actually "window is open, isn't it?" but it's a full-height window so I think in english door works better}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Korekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in their right mind would leave it open?{/who opened it}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I can pull off something like this.{/should have backed down/stopped after all}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-san, still nothing?{/again? - still  no clue what they are playing or what's this about}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to think my next moves through!{/I am now thinking which one would be the best}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone locked the door!{/it's locked}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}If I stay outside even a bit longer...{/like this}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-san, still nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you I'm thinking it through, you dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get through...{/it's no use}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how I'll meet my end - on this veranda?{/at this rate, at this veranda, I...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still count on Iyona-chan!{/definitely, if I ask iyona}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... This time, I'll get firm footing first.{lit: this time, walk/go well/skillfully}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! How come a blizzard \Nalso starts at a moment like this?!{/at such a time, also blizzard}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Iyona-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of divination are you looking for?{/what fortune-telling is your wish}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a little curious \Nabout the man I'm going to marry, so...{actually "let's see, my future lover/beloved one, or something like that..." but in english "lover" has other, less chaste meanings that doesn't quite match "koibito" which is rather pure in nature}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Now, if you just let me...{/leave this to me}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.67,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuffle! Shuffle! Shuffle! Shuffle!{guess, most likely ura is something about fortune telling so "divinate, divinate" or smt like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:46.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H021114&\3c&H159CAE&\blur1\b1\bord3}Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a snowman!{/yeti}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A snowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you quite sure?{for real/true?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,More than sure! I've seen him with my own eyes, \Noutside the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be still somewhere around here!{/he is totally still somewhere in this area}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, he's not getting away!{half guess, machi/mate kinda has to do with "wait"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me please, Taruruuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can still catch him.{/must be still in this vicinity}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, snowman! \NIf you really are a man, show yourself now!{/don't hide and come out}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already sure that was the end of me.{/I thought I would die}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui-chan, are you sure your eyes \Ndidn't play a trick on you?{/is it possible you mistook it for something else/misperceived it}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming back already!{/returning}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto! We can't let Iyona-chan see me here!{/find/discover}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, right here, \NI need a magic for staying in this room!{/like this, in this room to be - isn't there a magic for that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly shouldn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still remember seeing it so vividly!{/after all I saw it so clearly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, Taru! \NDo something, anything to save me now!{/sooner}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I cooled my head a bit.{"to pull oneself together; to collect oneself (after a failure); to regain control (of oneself)"}\NShall we resume with the divination, Iyona-chan?{/let's continue with fortune-telling}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we have a cushion like that before?{/since when do we have ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Honmaru, this is Concushion Magic.{absolute guess, I can't find this chapter and it's not in wiki either, would assume the last part of it is "kushon" but still no idea what is "shi/se" in the beginning; with previous such titles in mind, it must be some verb that is spelled shi/se as oniyomi but that's like looking for a needle in a haystack}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns anyone into a cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:26.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,0)\b1\blur1\bord1\fs30\c&HA981BE&\1a&H44&\3c&H4E2A65&\3a&H42&}Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, well and truly, \Nthe Great Magician Taruruuto-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we...{/anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I resume{the divination} from where we left off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan is sitting on Taru's cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous, Taru!{/envy}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan's future husband
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,would be really tall and hefty, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?{/really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll have yet to grow \Nmuch taller than this!{/definitely, I will grow much taller in the future}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll even grow tall enough \Nto become a basketball pro!{/I should become a basketball player}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One and two, and three, and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it seems, the guy would be mighty rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, I'll have yet to discover a new oilfield!{/I will definitely dig up/strike/stumble oil in the future}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe even Harako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Rui-chan, you're going too far...{unsure what she means, "I don't like it, if it's rui-chan..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way it can be Harako! \N'Cause it's me! Right here!{/no reason for it to be harako}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And also handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is tall, with deep pockets and handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And he is right here.{/I'm here}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, from what I can tell, \Nhe is not a boy from our class, that's for sure.{/at least, it shouldn't be a boy from out class}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,With this next card, \Nwe'll find out what this guy's initials are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually a bit scared to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no doubt, it's H for Honmaru.{/it's already decided}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then I'm flipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait though. If it's E for Edojo, \Nthat would be cool, too... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, Iyona-chan?{/you're fine with it}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:06.44,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000795&\blur0.6\bord1\b1}Bang~{bakon}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... divination!{guess, "iya ano sono ????" TLC} {11:11: I'm hearing いや、あの、その、あんがっ！\NThis is ususally said by a character who's having trouble finding words due to embarrasement/shock etc...\NA standard TL would be something like "Uh... Well... You see... I..." or any variation on this.\NAs long as it's incoherent it should be fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be cheerful about.{/no reason to cheer up}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up! Honmaru-kun! \NWhat are you doing here, of all places?{/in a place liek this}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You hid in the room \Nso you could spy on later while we change!{this sounds kinda redundant in japanese: secretly, concealed yourself/covertly hid}{ isn't that so?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like that! It's not like that at all! \NNot a word of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can explain, Iyona-chan!{/it's true}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally realized it.{/understood it now}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it after changing or after divination, \Npeeping is still peeping. An unworthy misdeed.{/dirty act}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not something a hero would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ask Iyona-chan to forgive me once more.{/apologize once again}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You can do it, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about what happened{/earlier}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm convinced that peeping into a girl's room \Nis something only the most unworthy man would do.{/is the worst the man can do}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, when I learned \Nyou'd be doing a love divination...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't help it.{/I became curious/obsessed/this gotten under my skin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.{/it's okay already}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I turned your divination \Ninto a hullabaloo!{sekkaku here is something along the lines "very sacred/precious/laborious/pressing" but unfortunately I have to drop it}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say it's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I had already found out \Nwho the man is that I'll be marrying.{she says "I now understood who is the person I love" so I think she means she is already in love with honmaru, not in the future, but previously I used husband and... this is becoming increasingly hard to put in words in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be constantly worried \Nabout whether or not this person would love me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I feel so relieved and refreshed!{/"I wonder, will this person become my lover or not" - my heart no longer throbs when thinking about that}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
